title: Diplomatas x Converse Rubber Tracks Brasil Mural
description:
We partnered with the São Paulo based street artist duo, Diplomatas, to create a hand painted mural for the Converse Rubber Tracks Brasil pop-up studio.
Check this out to see how it came to life.
